# Pin the stamp-script test fixtures to LF in every working tree.
#
# This repo runs with core.autocrlf=true, so a fresh checkout/clone would
# otherwise re-materialize these LF-stored fixtures as CRLF. That (a) breaks
# the premise of test_stamp.py::TestLineEndingPreservation and (b) makes every
# fresh checkout show spurious CRLF diffs that stage to no-ops.
# `text eol=lf` keeps them normalized LF on commit and forces LF on checkout
# regardless of the user's autocrlf setting.
orchestration/skills/orchestrating/scripts/tests-fixtures/** text eol=lf
